That's a start.

1097
01:34:00,380 --> 01:34:03,465
I'm at the Albert now.
I'll be looking for you.

1098
01:34:23,335 --> 01:34:24,346
Come on, Stella, let's go.

1099
01:34:24,385 --> 01:34:26,428
One of you keep an eye on this window.

1100
01:34:26,469 --> 01:34:29,562
